WEBVTT

01:38.110 --> 01:40.630
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.320 --> 01:43.710
[Episode 26]

02:30.680 --> 02:31.280
Let's go.

03:21.190 --> 03:22.050
What happened?

03:23.190 --> 03:23.960
It's no use.

03:24.910 --> 03:26.040
They can't be saved.

03:26.470 --> 03:28.360
We all took the Mind-Awakening Pills.

03:28.360 --> 03:29.490
Taking too much of it

03:30.329 --> 03:31.930
damages the heart meridian.

03:49.430 --> 03:50.490
What are you doing?

04:19.600 --> 04:20.730
Lord of Rust-Sword,

04:21.430 --> 04:23.560
your kindness to the Wushuang Society

04:23.680 --> 04:25.610
can only be repaid in the next life.

04:26.830 --> 04:28.630
For the future of the human race,

04:29.270 --> 04:31.510
you must bring
the Unparalleled Secret Magic

04:31.510 --> 04:33.040
back to the Central Plains.

04:35.430 --> 04:37.890
You must bring it
back to the Central Plains.

04:38.159 --> 04:38.950
Please.

04:43.230 --> 04:47.159
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

04:47.840 --> 04:51.240
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

04:51.880 --> 04:55.710
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

04:53.430 --> 04:54.000
Go.

04:55.730 --> 04:58.970
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

04:59.260 --> 05:03.100
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

05:02.390 --> 05:04.360
Lord of Rust-Sword, please go now!

05:03.960 --> 05:07.720
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

05:04.950 --> 05:07.820
The immortal sect will catch up
if you don't hurry!

05:07.740 --> 05:11.460
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

05:11.490 --> 05:16.460
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

05:17.240 --> 05:19.280
♪ What do you think is ♪

05:19.300 --> 05:21.590
♪ The most impressive farewell
in the world? ♪

05:21.950 --> 05:25.090
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

05:25.920 --> 05:29.880
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

05:29.900 --> 05:33.130
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

05:33.680 --> 05:35.420
♪ When do you think ♪

05:35.440 --> 05:37.880
♪ The bloody strife will come to an end? ♪

05:37.900 --> 05:41.220
♪ Burn myself to prove it
without looking back ♪

05:41.770 --> 05:45.750
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

05:45.780 --> 05:51.960
♪ The dawn light
illuminates the vast sky ♪

05:57.070 --> 06:01.160
There is a path to heaven in the books.

06:02.040 --> 06:05.680
Why bother seeking immortals
on Penglai Island?

06:05.390 --> 06:09.320
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

06:06.720 --> 06:09.870
I will return riding the wind.

06:10.110 --> 06:13.520
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

06:10.510 --> 06:16.190
Away from this ever-changing world.

06:14.020 --> 06:17.850
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

06:17.870 --> 06:21.100
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

06:21.150 --> 06:24.990
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

06:25.850 --> 06:29.610
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

06:29.630 --> 06:33.350
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

06:33.370 --> 06:37.030
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

06:37.150 --> 06:39.190
♪ What do you think is ♪

06:39.210 --> 06:41.500
♪ The most impressive farewell
in the world? ♪

06:41.830 --> 06:44.800
♪ End these everlasting battles ♪

06:45.680 --> 06:49.610
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

06:49.750 --> 06:54.030
♪ Someone's got to clean up this mess ♪

06:57.920 --> 06:58.720
Tai Shiqian.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.720
He took the Mind-Awakening Pills.

07:21.720 --> 07:22.450
What is that?

07:22.830 --> 07:23.750
A pill that can instantly

07:23.750 --> 07:25.280
awaken one's mental power.

07:25.390 --> 07:26.590
But if taken too much,

07:26.800 --> 07:27.800
it will backfire,

07:28.680 --> 07:30.040
destroy the heart and meridians,

07:30.040 --> 07:31.500
and lead to certain death.

07:45.040 --> 07:46.170
Lord of Rust-Sword!

07:46.430 --> 07:47.490
Don't come closer.

07:51.000 --> 07:52.070
It's dangerous.

07:52.800 --> 07:53.659
Leave me alone.

07:56.390 --> 07:57.520
Leave.

08:08.780 --> 08:10.390
You've finally come.

08:55.710 --> 08:57.230
Miss Sheng, are you okay?

09:00.280 --> 09:00.750
Oh no.

09:01.030 --> 09:03.760
The people from the Tianyuan Sect
have caught up.

09:04.440 --> 09:04.970
Let's go!

09:28.000 --> 09:28.790
Right ahead.

09:51.150 --> 09:52.440
You are so hard to kill.

09:53.720 --> 09:54.720
You bunch of ants.

09:55.540 --> 09:56.890
You should have hidden in the dark ditch

09:56.890 --> 09:58.870
and curled up for the rest of your lives.

09:58.870 --> 10:00.530
But you insisted on coming out

10:00.550 --> 10:01.870
and annoying me.

10:05.790 --> 10:06.600
You lot

10:08.110 --> 10:09.360
should have been crushed

10:09.360 --> 10:10.360
under my foot long ago.

10:10.360 --> 10:11.240
How dare you drag out
your feeble existence

10:11.240 --> 10:12.120
to this day?

10:12.630 --> 10:13.240
Today,

10:13.840 --> 10:15.440
if I don't skin you alive

10:15.440 --> 10:16.120
and tear you apart,

10:16.120 --> 10:18.120
how can I vent the hatred in my heart?

10:19.550 --> 10:20.360
At first,

10:20.870 --> 10:22.510
I just wanted to be an ordinary person.

10:22.510 --> 10:23.840
But then I remember that
someone like you,

10:23.840 --> 10:24.910
neither human nor demon,

10:24.910 --> 10:26.440
still exists in this world.

10:26.600 --> 10:28.530
You're like a maggot in the gutter,

10:28.630 --> 10:29.890
disgusting to look at.

10:40.870 --> 10:41.800
If you don't die,

10:41.990 --> 10:43.250
how can I be satisfied?

11:19.750 --> 11:21.480
You're but a mere Nascent Soul.

13:27.080 --> 13:28.790
Look at your pathetic state.

13:29.000 --> 13:31.080
You were supposed to be
the strongest War Demon,

13:31.080 --> 13:32.600
yet you insisted on being a human.

13:32.600 --> 13:33.860
You gave up your power,

13:33.870 --> 13:35.320
pushed yourself to this state,

13:35.320 --> 13:36.510
and are now at the mercy of others.

13:36.510 --> 13:38.440
How does it feel to lose your power?

13:38.840 --> 13:40.630
You can't even protect yourself.

13:40.630 --> 13:41.600
Lu Qianqiao,

13:41.790 --> 13:43.210
you are nothing but trash.

13:43.210 --> 13:44.440
You are nothing but trash.

13:44.440 --> 13:45.360
You are nothing but trash!

13:45.360 --> 13:46.820
You are nothing but trash!

15:07.240 --> 15:08.000
You...

15:21.090 --> 15:23.090
Look at you, so eager to see me.

15:23.960 --> 15:25.270
Did you miss me?

15:27.030 --> 15:28.090
Where is my friend?

15:29.320 --> 15:30.080
Friend?

15:33.270 --> 15:35.130
Are you really that incompetent?

15:35.600 --> 15:37.080
After all this time,

15:37.750 --> 15:39.440
she is still just your friend?

15:40.750 --> 15:41.950
Where exactly is she?

15:42.600 --> 15:43.460
Want to see her?

15:44.480 --> 15:45.150
Follow me.

16:23.710 --> 16:24.910
After all, Xia Xuanzi

16:24.960 --> 16:26.600
is at the Void Stage,

16:26.600 --> 16:28.630
and a long-established Gu master.

16:28.870 --> 16:30.470
Even if you two Nascent Souls

16:30.510 --> 16:31.640
fought to the death,

16:31.750 --> 16:33.010
it'd have been futile.

16:34.080 --> 16:36.540
This young lady was hit by
the Bone-Eroding,

16:36.870 --> 16:37.870
Blood-Averting,

16:38.200 --> 16:39.080
and Dream-Crashing

16:39.080 --> 16:40.150
Gu poisons.

16:40.630 --> 16:42.670
Logically, she shouldn't be alive.

16:43.480 --> 16:44.960
But I found

16:45.200 --> 16:46.660
a strange power in her body

16:47.150 --> 16:48.950
protecting her last bit of life.

16:49.320 --> 16:51.390
I used the Giant Spirit Fruit
as the main ingredient,

16:51.390 --> 16:53.850
supplemented with Immortal Ginseng Grass,

16:54.030 --> 16:54.960
Red Velvet Lamp,

16:55.150 --> 16:56.080
Green Chiretta,

16:56.360 --> 16:57.440
and Corydalis

16:57.960 --> 16:59.760
to expel the Gu and detoxify her.

16:59.790 --> 17:00.790
Just yesterday,

17:01.030 --> 17:02.440
I've already expelled

17:02.790 --> 17:04.190
the Gu bugs from her body.

17:04.400 --> 17:06.640
Once the residual poison is cleared,

17:07.200 --> 17:08.720
she will wake up soon.

17:10.630 --> 17:13.640
Bone-Eroding and Dream-Crashing
poisons are easy to cure.

17:13.640 --> 17:14.770
But Blood-Averting

17:15.000 --> 17:17.240
will attach itself to the blood vessels
and meridians.

17:17.240 --> 17:18.170
Using Corydalis

17:18.170 --> 17:19.970
can never remove it completely.

17:22.270 --> 17:23.069
Corydalis

17:23.440 --> 17:24.700
has a strong and fierce

17:24.720 --> 17:25.920
medicinal property.

17:25.920 --> 17:27.980
This young lady is severely injured.

17:28.400 --> 17:30.060
If the wrong medicine is used,

17:30.720 --> 17:32.110
it will backfire.

17:33.160 --> 17:33.790
So,

17:34.620 --> 17:36.350
we should use Wugen fruit instead.

17:36.350 --> 17:37.640
Grind it into powder
and dissolve it in water.

17:37.640 --> 17:39.840
The water should be hot but not boiling.

17:42.270 --> 17:44.000
I didn't expect you

17:44.440 --> 17:46.720
to be an expert in pharmacology.

17:48.960 --> 17:50.750
Thank you for saving us.

17:51.310 --> 17:52.240
You are welcome.

17:52.920 --> 17:54.030
Xia Xuanzi

17:54.270 --> 17:56.030
is known as the world's best

17:56.200 --> 17:57.440
Gu master.

17:58.030 --> 18:00.230
To be able to dispel
the Gu poison he cast

18:00.590 --> 18:01.590
is also

18:02.270 --> 18:04.000
a pleasure for me.

18:06.830 --> 18:07.550
May I know

18:08.160 --> 18:09.070
who you are?

18:11.160 --> 18:12.960
I'm the master of Qinghong Sect,

18:13.400 --> 18:14.270
Fu Tian.

18:40.640 --> 18:41.240
Have a sip.

18:44.550 --> 18:46.750
You mean, this is the Qinghong Sect?

18:47.880 --> 18:48.590
Yes.

18:49.920 --> 18:51.520
But when I passed by just now,

18:51.680 --> 18:52.880
I saw many craftsmen.

18:54.590 --> 18:55.920
You should be aware that

18:56.200 --> 18:58.000
North Xiang is famous for paper.

18:58.790 --> 18:59.310
Yes.

19:00.200 --> 19:01.160
Our paper mill

19:01.680 --> 19:02.540
has a history of

19:02.790 --> 19:04.510
more than 200 years.

19:05.240 --> 19:06.550
The paper we produce is

19:06.720 --> 19:08.720
thin and even,

19:09.000 --> 19:10.640
white as fine jade,

19:11.160 --> 19:12.240
soft and dense,

19:12.720 --> 19:14.400
insect-proof and heat-resistant.

19:14.400 --> 19:15.640
It's absorbent and dries quickly.

19:15.640 --> 19:17.570
Ink remains vibrant on its surface

19:17.750 --> 19:19.150
and does not fade easily.

19:19.440 --> 19:22.200
It sells very well in the market.

19:24.640 --> 19:25.550
Papermaking?

19:27.070 --> 19:28.730
Isn't this the Qinghong Sect?

19:30.030 --> 19:32.360
Qinghong Sect needs to eat and drink, too.

19:32.830 --> 19:34.070
Without industry

19:34.350 --> 19:35.160
and income,

19:35.510 --> 19:36.790
how can we live?

19:41.920 --> 19:44.270
I know you have some thoughts.

19:44.720 --> 19:46.480
I also know a little about your grudge

19:46.480 --> 19:47.880
against my sect.

19:48.750 --> 19:50.160
But I lack the power

19:50.640 --> 19:52.270
to stop it.

19:52.830 --> 19:54.160
You are the Sect Master,

19:54.400 --> 19:55.640
but you lack the power to act?

19:55.640 --> 19:56.400
Yes.

19:58.160 --> 19:59.510
If one cannot control

19:59.550 --> 20:00.830
the sect members,

20:02.240 --> 20:03.700
then being the Sect Master

20:03.920 --> 20:06.110
is just an empty title.

20:06.880 --> 20:09.070
Any faction in its development

20:09.590 --> 20:11.640
will have some deviations.

20:12.480 --> 20:14.440
A few Dharma Kings

20:14.680 --> 20:16.000
and Branch Masters of our sect

20:16.000 --> 20:17.510
strongly opposed my

20:18.270 --> 20:20.960
benevolent philosophy.

20:21.790 --> 20:23.320
They bewitched the members

20:24.310 --> 20:26.040
and broke free from my control.

20:27.350 --> 20:28.610
Then how do you explain

20:28.960 --> 20:30.360
Bishui Branch's action?

20:31.240 --> 20:33.400
The Bishui Branch's Master and Gui

20:35.110 --> 20:36.640
are both their operatives.

20:37.680 --> 20:38.830
But if it weren't for

20:38.830 --> 20:40.550
the two Protectors and the support

20:40.550 --> 20:43.440
of the Dharma Kings and Vajras this time,

20:44.590 --> 20:46.880
I couldn't have kept this paper mill,

20:47.440 --> 20:48.550
let alone

20:48.790 --> 20:50.750
the financial resources of our sect.

20:50.750 --> 20:52.400
I'm afraid even my title

20:53.240 --> 20:55.370
would have been taken by someone else.

20:56.640 --> 20:58.960
If our sect were united

20:58.960 --> 21:00.220
and working together,

21:00.310 --> 21:01.830
the people of the immortal sect

21:01.830 --> 21:04.830
wouldn't have dared
to cross the border and invade us.

21:05.440 --> 21:06.400
They burned down the Sihe Library

21:06.400 --> 21:08.510
that our sect had operated for years.

21:09.400 --> 21:10.920
By the time we rushed over,

21:11.920 --> 21:13.270
it was too late.

21:13.720 --> 21:15.110
The ancient books of a thousand years

21:15.110 --> 21:16.440
were destroyed in a day.

21:17.750 --> 21:19.400
We only had time to save you

21:19.470 --> 21:20.790
and that young lady.

21:24.750 --> 21:25.720
I have a friend

21:26.350 --> 21:27.810
named Lord of Rust-Sword.

21:28.440 --> 21:29.700
Do you know where he is?

21:43.270 --> 21:44.480
The ones buried here

21:44.880 --> 21:46.810
are all from the Wushuang Society.

21:47.030 --> 21:48.510
We don't have their names,

21:48.720 --> 21:50.920
so we didn't set up tombstones for them.

21:56.790 --> 21:58.590
Here lies a young lady

21:59.070 --> 22:00.070
in her twenties.

22:00.480 --> 22:02.080
She looked somewhat pretty.

22:02.790 --> 22:04.000
She used a sword.

22:04.880 --> 22:07.350
So we buried her together with it.

22:57.720 --> 23:00.530
[Xutuo City]

23:01.030 --> 23:01.680
Hurry up.

23:01.920 --> 23:02.780
Hurry up, guys.

23:04.550 --> 23:05.070
Boss.

23:06.240 --> 23:07.680
When will your caravan leave the city?

23:07.680 --> 23:08.680
Tomorrow at noon.

23:09.380 --> 23:10.210
I have 2 friends

23:10.210 --> 23:11.440
who want to travel to the Central Plains.

23:11.440 --> 23:13.510
Bring your own carriage.
To get past the pass,

23:13.510 --> 23:14.840
it's 2 taels per person.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.230
Here is the deposit.

23:16.230 --> 23:17.690
Where do we meet tomorrow?

23:18.400 --> 23:19.160
Right here.

23:20.510 --> 23:20.920
Okay.

23:25.880 --> 23:26.310
Hurry.

23:29.350 --> 23:30.750
Come and take a look.

23:39.410 --> 23:40.370
Cantaloupes.

23:40.400 --> 23:41.860
Free if they aren't sweet!

23:46.430 --> 23:47.790
She must have spotted us.

23:47.790 --> 23:48.390
After her!

24:02.510 --> 24:03.270
Tang,

24:03.680 --> 24:04.940
how are your injuries?

24:05.160 --> 24:05.690
I'm fine.

24:06.680 --> 24:07.510
What about the books?

24:07.510 --> 24:08.160
Did you count them?

24:08.160 --> 24:08.960
Are they all here?

24:08.960 --> 24:09.880
Yes, they are.

24:11.440 --> 24:12.170
That's good.

24:17.710 --> 24:18.270
Who is it?

24:18.790 --> 24:19.240
Me.

24:25.510 --> 24:26.960
The people from the immortal sect
have caught up.

24:26.960 --> 24:28.490
We must leave immediately.

24:39.880 --> 24:41.480
Your yin energy is stagnant,

24:41.580 --> 24:42.910
and your pulse is rapid.

24:43.920 --> 24:46.450
It seems the Blood-Averting Gu poison
hasn't been cleared.

24:46.450 --> 24:47.650
It's still acting up.

25:27.960 --> 25:29.620
I hope I'm not disturbing you.

25:39.790 --> 25:41.240
Song, who delivers the food,

25:41.240 --> 25:42.700
was injured this morning.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.600
I told him to go back and rest.

25:44.720 --> 25:45.680
Since I was on my way,

25:45.680 --> 25:46.740
I brought this food

25:46.920 --> 25:48.000
over to you.

25:49.880 --> 25:50.720
Beef noodles

25:51.000 --> 25:52.000
and Suquan wine.

25:52.590 --> 25:53.510
I don't know

25:53.920 --> 25:55.180
if it suits your taste.

25:57.830 --> 25:58.750
Thank you, Sect Master.

25:58.750 --> 25:59.350
All right.

26:00.440 --> 26:01.370
You're welcome.

26:01.960 --> 26:03.620
You are not a member of my sect.

26:03.750 --> 26:05.810
You don't need to call me Sect Master.

26:05.880 --> 26:06.740
Just call me...

26:09.270 --> 26:10.620
Just call me Fu Tian.

26:15.480 --> 26:17.830
I feel a connection with you

26:18.480 --> 26:20.340
and want to make friends with you.

26:20.590 --> 26:21.520
Can I call you...

26:22.160 --> 26:24.030
Can I call you Lu?

26:25.720 --> 26:26.270
Sure.

26:28.160 --> 26:28.830
Thank you.

26:37.590 --> 26:40.270
Are the noodles not to your taste?

26:42.590 --> 26:43.450
I'm not hungry.

26:44.440 --> 26:45.510
That's a pity.

26:46.070 --> 26:47.070
My chef

26:47.440 --> 26:49.270
cooks very well.

26:53.030 --> 26:54.310
Look at this food box.

26:54.790 --> 26:56.450
Its insulation is excellent.

26:57.200 --> 26:58.400
Let me put it this way,

26:58.510 --> 27:01.910
from the moment the noodles
leave the pot to when you eat them,

27:02.060 --> 27:03.990
the temperature won't drop at all.

27:05.070 --> 27:06.350
Look at this lid.

27:07.000 --> 27:08.930
It has a spiral pattern on the rims.

27:09.400 --> 27:10.030
Cover it,

27:10.640 --> 27:11.500
twist it tight,

27:11.790 --> 27:13.190
and it becomes airtight.

27:13.510 --> 27:14.680
Look at this food box again.

27:14.680 --> 27:16.510
It has double walls.

27:16.790 --> 27:19.350
In the gap between the two walls,

27:19.680 --> 27:21.720
if you put in hot water and cover it,

27:22.510 --> 27:24.350
no matter what you put inside,

27:24.590 --> 27:25.640
it will remain hot

27:26.240 --> 27:27.240
for 4 hours.

27:29.750 --> 27:31.080
It really is exquisite.

27:31.720 --> 27:33.050
Such a delicate object.

27:33.400 --> 27:35.200
If it weren't for Goddess Wushuang

27:35.200 --> 27:36.240
designing it,

27:36.400 --> 27:37.750
I'm afraid we would never

27:37.750 --> 27:40.210
have had the fortune
to enjoy it in this life.

27:41.920 --> 27:42.980
Goddess Wushuang?

27:45.680 --> 27:46.960
Do you mean that

27:47.440 --> 27:50.240
Qinghong Sect has the
Unparalleled Secret Magic?

27:50.790 --> 27:51.270
Yes.

27:52.000 --> 27:53.200
Back then, when I read

27:53.200 --> 27:55.000
the Unparalleled Secret Magic,

27:55.510 --> 27:56.750
I felt some of the things in it

27:56.750 --> 27:57.590
could be used in daily life,

27:57.590 --> 27:58.920
so I recorded them.

27:59.680 --> 28:00.960
I don't know

28:01.070 --> 28:02.160
if I can still find

28:02.480 --> 28:03.830
the original notes now.

28:05.720 --> 28:07.720
Even a single word or sentence
would be good.

28:07.720 --> 28:08.450
Sect Master,

28:08.830 --> 28:10.270
could you help me look for it?

28:10.270 --> 28:10.920
Sure.

28:21.440 --> 28:22.240
Lu,

28:23.240 --> 28:25.440
these are just some random notes I took.

28:25.640 --> 28:26.900
They are not complete.

28:28.590 --> 28:29.590
If you need,

28:29.590 --> 28:31.310
I'll send someone to look for more.

28:31.310 --> 28:33.510
Maybe we can still find some

28:33.790 --> 28:35.120
surviving woodblocks.

28:36.070 --> 28:37.400
Thank you, Sect Master.

28:38.510 --> 28:39.270
Lu,

28:39.480 --> 28:41.070
you don't need to be so polite.

28:41.070 --> 28:43.510
In fact, helping you is helping myself.

28:44.200 --> 28:45.240
The Sihe Library

28:45.550 --> 28:47.750
was the lifeblood of our Qinghong Sect.

28:48.270 --> 28:50.030
Many of the books

28:50.680 --> 28:51.830
and collections inside

28:51.830 --> 28:53.490
were already lost to history.

28:53.720 --> 28:55.980
The destruction of the library this time

28:56.270 --> 28:57.510
breaks my heart.

28:58.480 --> 28:59.920
As for those books,

29:00.110 --> 29:00.960
I don't know

29:01.160 --> 29:02.400
how many generations

29:02.640 --> 29:04.480
of time and effort it will take

29:04.720 --> 29:07.070
to fully restore them.

29:09.400 --> 29:10.160
If there is anything

29:10.160 --> 29:11.360
you need my help with,

29:11.590 --> 29:12.350
just ask.

29:15.440 --> 29:17.040
I actually do have something

29:17.110 --> 29:18.440
to trouble you with, Lu.

29:27.310 --> 29:28.400
For Miss Xin's body

29:28.400 --> 29:29.510
to fully recover,

29:29.510 --> 29:30.830
it will take some time.

29:31.110 --> 29:32.270
While you wait,

29:32.510 --> 29:34.070
could you help me translate some

29:34.070 --> 29:34.930
ancient books?

29:49.110 --> 29:49.880
This is...

29:50.750 --> 29:52.160
A War Demon book.

29:55.350 --> 29:55.920
What?

29:56.400 --> 29:58.960
Are War Demon books not books?

30:01.880 --> 30:03.480
For the inheritance of civilization,

30:03.480 --> 30:05.680
the books and language of the War Demons

30:06.110 --> 30:08.550
are also a part of civilization

30:08.840 --> 30:10.600
and should be passed down.

30:15.240 --> 30:16.440
How are you so sure

30:16.790 --> 30:17.750
that I'd know

30:18.030 --> 30:19.760
the language of the War Demons?

30:19.880 --> 30:22.010
War Demons have vigorous blood and qi.

30:22.270 --> 30:24.000
Their pulse is large but gentle

30:24.200 --> 30:24.880
and calm.

30:25.640 --> 30:27.700
All 3 parts of their wrists are large.

30:27.830 --> 30:30.790
They are innately 100 times stronger
than normal people.

30:30.790 --> 30:32.350
Anyone with some medical knowledge

30:32.350 --> 30:33.480
can easily discover

30:33.860 --> 30:35.290
your identity, Lu.

30:35.880 --> 30:36.960
Since you knew,

30:37.110 --> 30:38.510
why did you still save me?

30:39.730 --> 30:41.650
I feel a connection with you.

30:42.350 --> 30:43.960
I want to be your friend.

30:45.590 --> 30:47.030
Even if I am a War Demon?

30:47.400 --> 30:48.860
Even if you are a War Demon.

30:54.030 --> 30:55.110
Meeting you today

30:56.240 --> 30:58.350
feels like catching up with an old friend.

30:58.350 --> 30:59.000
Lu,

30:59.830 --> 31:01.230
whether you agree or not,

31:01.790 --> 31:03.550
I want to be your friend.

31:12.960 --> 31:13.440
Okay.

31:14.480 --> 31:15.160
I agree.

31:17.200 --> 31:17.830
Thank you.

31:39.550 --> 31:41.350
I saw Tai Shiqian and the others.

31:42.510 --> 31:44.910
The Qinghong Sect collected their remains

31:45.270 --> 31:47.070
and built tombs and steles for them

31:47.070 --> 31:48.670
right behind the paper mill.

31:50.070 --> 31:51.000
When you wake up,

31:51.550 --> 31:52.550
I'll take you

31:52.920 --> 31:54.320
to burn incense for them.

31:59.240 --> 32:00.750
I found that the Qinghong Sect

32:00.750 --> 32:01.790
has some surviving

32:01.790 --> 32:03.480
woodblocks of Unparalleled Secret Magic.

32:03.480 --> 32:04.270
Fu Tian said

32:04.790 --> 32:05.750
he will go to the warehouse tomorrow

32:05.750 --> 32:07.080
to help me look for them.

32:07.750 --> 32:09.280
If Lord of Rust-Sword knew,

32:09.590 --> 32:10.830
he'd have been happy.

32:17.550 --> 32:18.310
Xin Mei,

32:20.350 --> 32:21.400
wake up soon.

32:39.640 --> 32:40.500
Want some wine?

32:47.070 --> 32:48.000
Care for a drink?

32:50.440 --> 32:51.640
When did you get here?

32:53.270 --> 32:54.070
Lu Qianqiao,

32:55.480 --> 32:57.000
why do you like her so much?

32:58.110 --> 32:59.070
If you came to me

32:59.200 --> 33:00.070
just to talk about such

33:00.070 --> 33:01.070
boring nonsense,

33:01.640 --> 33:03.310
then you should find someone else.

33:03.310 --> 33:04.370
I was just kidding.

33:06.640 --> 33:07.700
Are you really mad?

33:09.640 --> 33:11.170
In a Qinghong Sect this big,

33:11.310 --> 33:13.370
is there no one else you can chat with?

33:15.510 --> 33:16.680
There used to be.

33:17.880 --> 33:18.720
But

33:19.200 --> 33:22.600
they were killed by the immortal sects
of the Central Plains.

33:24.000 --> 33:24.600
I'm sorry.

33:24.830 --> 33:25.630
It's nothing.

33:25.880 --> 33:27.010
I have many enemies;

33:27.790 --> 33:29.550
there's always hatred
going back and forth.

33:29.550 --> 33:30.950
It's good to have someone

33:31.000 --> 33:32.330
dig up old scores for me.

33:37.200 --> 33:38.600
What are your plans next?

33:39.880 --> 33:41.080
When Xin Mei wakes up,

33:41.590 --> 33:43.190
I'll take her away from here.

33:43.550 --> 33:44.110
Where to?

33:45.310 --> 33:46.840
Back to the Central Plains.

33:48.640 --> 33:49.350
Homesick?

33:51.160 --> 33:52.220
I don't have a home.

33:54.240 --> 33:55.370
What a coincidence.

33:56.110 --> 33:57.570
I don't have a home either.

33:58.620 --> 34:00.420
Our backgrounds match so well,

34:01.350 --> 34:03.750
we really are a match made in heaven.

34:10.510 --> 34:11.400
Lu Qianqiao,

34:12.070 --> 34:13.110
do you still remember

34:13.110 --> 34:14.639
what your home looked like?

34:20.590 --> 34:21.400
I remember.

34:22.440 --> 34:23.190
In my home,

34:24.230 --> 34:26.150
there was a big, round moon,

34:27.920 --> 34:29.110
just like this one.

34:34.880 --> 34:35.590
Isn't the moon like this

34:35.590 --> 34:36.590
everywhere?

34:37.550 --> 34:38.480
It's different.

34:39.840 --> 34:42.239
The moon at home
was exceptionally bright.

34:43.550 --> 34:45.320
Even without lighting a candle,

34:45.320 --> 34:47.580
you could see the whole village clearly.

34:49.230 --> 34:50.070
I remember

34:51.000 --> 34:52.150
lying on the grass.

34:53.760 --> 34:55.800
The wind blowing through my fingertips

34:55.800 --> 34:57.630
was sweet and fragrant.

34:58.510 --> 35:00.110
The flowers at home were red.

35:00.510 --> 35:01.800
They blossomed vibrantly,

35:01.800 --> 35:03.530
covering the entire hillside.

35:04.440 --> 35:06.000
When I looked up at the sky,

35:06.590 --> 35:08.880
I only saw waves rolling on the horizon,

35:09.320 --> 35:10.320
endlessly green.

35:12.400 --> 35:13.150
Lu Qianqiao,

35:14.400 --> 35:15.800
do you know where that is?

35:17.760 --> 35:19.020
That's your hometown.

35:19.230 --> 35:20.190
How would I know?

35:21.670 --> 35:22.400
That's true.

35:23.960 --> 35:25.280
Even I have forgotten.

35:25.840 --> 35:27.370
How could anyone else know?

35:40.130 --> 35:42.060
I almost forgot the real business.

35:42.260 --> 35:42.790
Let's go.

35:42.860 --> 35:44.590
I'll take you to see a good show.

35:51.840 --> 35:52.920
My good brother.

35:53.280 --> 35:54.590
Brother.

35:55.190 --> 35:57.920
We shall roam the martial world together.

35:58.440 --> 36:00.590
I'll listen to you, Brother.

36:02.630 --> 36:03.920
Master, he is here.

36:04.550 --> 36:05.320
Have a seat.

36:08.000 --> 36:09.550
Nice!

36:12.030 --> 36:13.840
The play just started.

36:14.230 --> 36:15.430
You're right on time.

36:16.280 --> 36:18.590
Do you also like watching plays, Lu?

36:20.030 --> 36:21.360
I haven't watched many.

36:21.710 --> 36:22.510
Why?

36:23.280 --> 36:25.710
Plays are all about
other people's stories.

36:25.710 --> 36:27.440
I don't like listening to them.

36:28.760 --> 36:30.160
If that's what you think,

36:30.800 --> 36:31.840
you're mistaken.

36:32.250 --> 36:33.130
Although plays

36:33.150 --> 36:34.550
are about others,

36:34.880 --> 36:36.480
if you really listen to them,

36:36.960 --> 36:38.030
you will find

36:38.400 --> 36:39.660
the lyrics expressive

36:39.960 --> 36:41.360
and the melody touching.

36:41.670 --> 36:43.150
Every frown, every smile,

36:43.360 --> 36:44.820
every action and movement

36:45.590 --> 36:49.230
seems to reflect your own heart.

36:49.880 --> 36:52.280
When the play ends
and the crowd disperses,

36:52.800 --> 36:55.630
you only feel a sense of sorrow.

36:56.190 --> 36:57.050
You cannot tell

36:57.280 --> 36:59.360
if the play is about yourself,

36:59.630 --> 37:02.960
or if you are already in the play.

37:09.550 --> 37:10.030
Please.

37:15.710 --> 37:16.880
It's so lively.

37:17.590 --> 37:19.320
What are they singing about?

37:20.760 --> 37:21.710
This play

37:22.280 --> 37:24.360
is about 2 friends

37:24.360 --> 37:25.710
who grew up together.

37:26.230 --> 37:29.150
They agreed to explore
the martial world together.

37:29.920 --> 37:31.450
Later, they got separated.

37:31.840 --> 37:32.840
One went south,

37:33.230 --> 37:34.630
and the other went north.

37:34.670 --> 37:35.840
Ten years later,

37:37.190 --> 37:38.320
they met again.

37:39.320 --> 37:40.840
One became a high official,

37:40.840 --> 37:42.030
but the other

37:43.710 --> 37:45.000
became a bandit.

37:51.710 --> 37:52.800
It really is

37:53.000 --> 37:54.190
a sorrowful story.

37:56.400 --> 37:57.440
Not only that.

37:58.760 --> 38:00.440
The child who became a bandit

38:00.760 --> 38:01.960
lost his memory

38:02.630 --> 38:03.960
and forgot everything.

38:06.920 --> 38:08.180
He forgot everything?

38:09.150 --> 38:09.800
Why?

38:11.630 --> 38:12.840
Perhaps along the way,

38:12.840 --> 38:14.840
he experienced too many hardships,

38:15.070 --> 38:16.070
couldn't bear it,

38:16.920 --> 38:18.920
and simply didn't want to remember.

38:23.590 --> 38:25.880
Listening closely, I feel so angry.

38:26.110 --> 38:28.760
These chattering people
are all scoundrels.

38:28.800 --> 38:31.630
Since ancient times, officials and bandits
have their fates intertwined.

38:31.630 --> 38:34.280
Kill the soldiers, sever the ties.

38:34.510 --> 38:36.440
It happens today.

38:40.670 --> 38:41.440
It's these

38:41.440 --> 38:43.370
friends-to-enemies plots again.

38:44.110 --> 38:44.960
So boring.

38:54.000 --> 38:55.550
Nice!

38:59.510 --> 39:00.070
Brother.

39:00.760 --> 39:03.030
Brother...

39:06.070 --> 39:06.960
He remembered.

39:09.150 --> 39:10.880
Unfortunately, it's too late.

39:10.920 --> 39:12.720
When a person dies, it's the end.

39:12.840 --> 39:14.240
They can never come back.

39:20.150 --> 39:21.550
There's a turning point.

39:22.590 --> 39:24.110
They went back to the past.

39:24.840 --> 39:27.440
This time, the child who became a bandit

39:27.840 --> 39:30.100
followed the official all the way north.

39:30.200 --> 39:31.400
They fought side by side

39:31.400 --> 39:33.000
and looked out for each other.

39:33.000 --> 39:35.200
They defeated strong enemies together

39:35.670 --> 39:38.230
and destroyed the oppressive dynasty.

39:40.760 --> 39:43.280
Fallen flowers may bloom again,

39:43.510 --> 39:46.440
but departed ones rarely return.

39:46.710 --> 39:50.550
The full moon before my eyes
sinks into the water,

39:50.710 --> 40:00.960
turning out to be an empty dream
without a trace.

40:24.230 --> 40:25.030
It's all fake.

40:28.030 --> 40:28.960
Yes.

40:30.270 --> 40:31.140
All of this

40:33.110 --> 40:34.230
was just the bandit's

40:34.230 --> 40:35.280
fantasy.

40:36.150 --> 40:37.440
His friend died

40:38.320 --> 40:39.780
and could never come back.

40:40.670 --> 40:41.400
Therefore,

40:41.760 --> 40:43.820
very few people watch this to the end.

40:45.400 --> 40:48.000
They just pretended that
time reversed itself

40:48.280 --> 40:50.480
and went back to that moment in the past,

40:50.760 --> 40:52.290
and took that as the ending.

40:57.440 --> 40:58.150
Lu.

40:59.510 --> 41:00.590
If it were you,

41:01.070 --> 41:03.200
would you rather be trapped in a dream,

41:03.960 --> 41:05.480
or return to the present

41:07.280 --> 41:09.030
and live a lonely life?

41:11.920 --> 41:12.920
In this world,

41:13.360 --> 41:15.400
there is no artifact to reverse time,

41:15.400 --> 41:17.000
nor is there a second chance.

41:17.670 --> 41:19.000
Once a decision is made,

41:19.070 --> 41:20.840
you should press forward
without hesitation

41:20.840 --> 41:21.770
and forge ahead.

41:22.360 --> 41:22.880
Right?

41:32.750 --> 41:34.110
When I was young,

41:37.320 --> 41:40.180
I also had a friend with whom
I shared life and death.

41:42.000 --> 41:42.860
Where is he now?

41:44.840 --> 41:46.640
I've not seen him in a long while.

41:48.320 --> 41:49.630
He might be long dead.

41:50.880 --> 41:51.590
Or perhaps,

41:53.440 --> 41:55.400
just like in this play,

41:56.480 --> 41:57.940
he has forgotten about me.

42:00.320 --> 42:01.190
I see.
